  <source>Nantes University Hospital</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to compare radiological behavior of blocks of macroporous
      phosphocalcium as bone substitute in comparison with iliac crest autograft in tibial valgus
      osteotomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
